[{"id":"RAW_ebdbcf7f","title":"全网最详细的 Codex 入门教程，手把手教你玩转 Vibe Coding。","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679828&idx=1&sn=6e1c0a935c70c566ee765c02a36327a6","date":"2026-02-09 01:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ebdbcf7f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"数字生命卡兹克","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":24,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_dd96812d","title":"Vibe Coding 在代码生成与协作中的实践与思考","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651275013&idx=2&sn=d696ab8030134d5251ce180ff5dbcd31","date":"2026-02-10 06:05:00","oneSentenceSummary":"阿里巴巴技术专家分享了 Vibe Coding 在大厂内部的落地实践，探讨了从 Copilot 向 Agent 演进中的质量控制、成本优化及国产模型适配方案。","summary":"本文整理自阿里巴巴高级技术专家向邦宇在 QCon 的演讲，深入探讨了 Vibe Coding（氛围编程）在阿里内部的演进与挑战。文章首先将 Vibe Coding 工具归纳为 Native IDE、插件、Web Agent 和 CLI 四类，并指出 Agent 模式在提升高频开发者产出方面效果显著。随后，作者重点分析了当前 AI 编程面临的代码质量（自洽性错误、安全漏洞）、调试困难（黑盒化）、上下文局限及高昂成本等核心痛点。针对这些问题，阿里团队提出了构建 Repo Wiki、建立 Agent 数据协议、任务模板化以及“Agent 即工具”等架构优化方案。此外，文章还详细分享了如何通过工程化手段（如死循环检测、格式修复）将国外 SOTA 模型替换为国产开源模型，以实现效能与成本的平衡。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_dd96812d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":36,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_4ead9a68","title":"Yelp 如何构建 “Yelp Assistant”","link":"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/how-yelp-built-yelp-assistant","date":"2026-02-09 16:31:03","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4ead9a68.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"ByteByteGo Newsletter","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_401505dd","title":"3 年、1 万人，快手技术团队首次系统披露 AI 研发范式升级历程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651274822&idx=1&sn=b4b364a2e23df2beda37e877001ea4df","date":"2026-02-09 05:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_401505dd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":59,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c72c00fd","title":"华为发布业界首个扩散语言模型 Agent，部分场景提速 8 倍！","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/378286.html","date":"2026-02-10 07:18:25","oneSentenceSummary":"华为联合多所高校发布业界首个扩散语言模型（DLLM）Agent，通过改变生成范式使 Agent 具备“全局规划”能力，执行速度最高提升 8 倍。","summary":"本文介绍了华为诺亚方舟实验室及其合作团队的最新研究成果《DLLM Agent: See Farther， Run Faster》。该研究通过严谨的对照实验证明，将 Agent 的底座从传统的自回归模型（AR）更换为扩散大模型（DLLM）后，Agent 在多轮推理和工具调用中表现出显著的效率优势。在准确率持平的前提下，DLLM Agent 的端到端执行速度平均提升 30% 以上，部分复杂任务提速达 8 倍。其核心优势在于 DLLM 能够实现“先全局、后细节”的规划模式，有效减少了 AR 模型因线性生成导致的路径偏差和冗余交互，为构建高效 Agent 提供了全新的设计维度。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c72c00fd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_41ca7ce7","title":"清华刘知远团队论文：最小化结构改动，短文本到长文本丝滑升级 | ICLR 2026","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODEzMjIyMA==&mid=2247731450&idx=2&sn=3894cd9c6cbb1819597afd469dbf1ce3","date":"2026-02-09 10:04:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41ca7ce7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技评论","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_48ab1cdc","title":"2026 年硅谷书单：18 位硅谷创始人共同推荐的 56 本书","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMDMxOTI2NA==&mid=2649104479&idx=1&sn=358e90989ecf328bc6bc47d22be5e315","date":"2026-02-09 09:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_48ab1cdc.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"十字路口Crossing","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_ed39a1a3","title":"快手用“对齐”技术，让广告推荐更懂你","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450953&idx=1&sn=47ed7abd6a494f4735154972fa1cf2e7","date":"2026-02-09 07:25:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ed39a1a3.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AINLP","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_7d30dbd7","title":"警钟敲响！Hinton 最新万字演讲：怒怼乔姆斯基、定义“不朽计算”、揭示人类唯一生路",