穴在上下文","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651275013&idx=1&sn=676ba2f122e957a2595dea61981f46e9","date":"2026-02-10 06:05:00","oneSentenceSummary":"前 OpenAI Codex 核心研发者 Calvin French-Owen 深度解析 Claude Code 的优势，强调上下文管理是 AI 编程的核心，并探讨了 AI 时代下工程师向“管理者”角色的转型。","summary":"本文整理了前 OpenAI 工程师、Codex 项目早期研发者 Calvin French-Owen 的播客访谈精华。他认为 Claude Code 通过创新的上下文拆分和子智能体协作机制，在处理复杂编程任务时表现优异，能将开发速度提升 5 倍。文章深入探讨了上下文窗口作为当前 AI 编程最大瓶颈的现状，分享了“金丝雀检测”和“主动清理”等实战技巧。同时，对比了 OpenAI（追求极致性能）与 Anthropic（追求好用的工具）的基因差异，并预言未来资深工程师将转型为“智能体团队管理者”，强调了自下而上的产品分发模式在开发者工具领域的决定性作用。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_eb9c50c3.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":62,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_9c115a8b","title":"别再让语音机器人“答非所问”：AI Force 任务型语音对话技术总结","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558288&idx=1&sn=1e34f7eae3421e09e8f2f78baeb5f066","date":"2026-02-10 00:32:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9c115a8b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_0fd403e0","title":"你是否遗漏了 Data Frame？Java 中 Data Frame 的力量","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/data-frames-java/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 15:02:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文探讨了 Java DataFrames 作为面向数据编程（DOP）中内存高效且易于维护的工具所展现的力量，弥合了底层性能与高层开发效率之间的鸿沟。","summary":"本文深入探讨了 DataFrames 在 Java 生态系统中的应用，特别是从面向数据编程（DOP）的角度出发。文章对比了 DOP 与传统的面向对象编程，认为将数据视为与逻辑分离的不可变状态在处理复杂数据操作时更具优势。作者以“十亿行挑战”（1BRC）为基准，将 DataFrame-EC 和 Tablesaw 等 Java 实现与 Python 的 pandas 以及 Kotlin 的 DataFrame 进行了对比。分析指出，虽然 Python 速度很快，但 Java DataFrames 通过原生类型集合和对象池技术提供了卓越的内存效率。此外，文章还展示了 DataFrame-EC 等库如何利用外部 DSL 使业务逻辑更具可读性和可外部化，最终将 Java DataFrames 定位为内存数据处理中替代数据库或 Spark 集群的稳健方案。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_0fd403e0.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_89098486","title":"Vercel 如何构建针对编程智能体的 AEO 追踪系统","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/how-we-built-aeo-tracking-for-coding-agents","date":"2026-02-09 13:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_89098486.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Vercel News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_16225284","title":"在资源受限的环境中构建 LLM：实战视角","link":"https://www.infoq.com/articles/building-llms-resource-constrained-environments/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_16225284.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_d05aef0d","title":"[视频播客] 与 Madelyn Olson 探讨 Valkey 的改进","link":"https://www.infoq.com/podcasts/valkey-performance-improvements/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-09 11:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d05aef0d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":30,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_f20403ee","title":"Flink ClickHouse Sink：生产级高可用写入方案｜得物技术","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&mid=2247542990&idx=1&sn=95c80d04da0238e8e16312f48c1a1f5f","date":"2026-02-09 10:36:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文详细介绍了得物技术针对 Flink 写入 ClickHouse 的生产级优化方案，通过本地表直写、数据量攒批及动态节点发现等手段解决开源 Sink 的性能与稳定性痛点。","summary":"文章深入剖析了 Flink 官方 ClickHouse Sink 在高并发场景下的三大痛点：内存占用不可控、不支持动态分表及分布式表写入性能瓶颈。针对这些问题，得物技术开发了一套高可用写入方案。核心改进包括：引入基于字节大小（metaSize）的攒批机制以防止 OOM；实现本地表直写并结合动态节点发现与故障剔除，提升吞吐并降低延迟；设计有界队列与线程池并发控制实现背压传导；通过递归重试与 Checkpoint 强刷机制，确保了 At-Least-Once 的数据一致性语义。此外，方案还支持按应用维度的动态路由与分表策略，满足了大规模多租户场景的需求。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f20403ee.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming